---
title: Turkey Scallopini and Risotto-Style Couscous with Roasted Brussels Sprouts and Squash
description: We've swapped out traditional arborio rice in this risotto for a 30 min cheat! Roasting shredded Brussels sprouts, creates crispy golden-brown flakes that add a unique crunch and flavour to this risotto. Sweet and nutty squash brings some welcome 'sunshine' and vitamin C to your autumn table. Enjoy!
